{"tid":1662732,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港文化] 點解無黃色酒樓嫁？","createTime":"2019-10-19T03:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T05:17:26.000Z","uid":48436,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0cce43ac7747c3a16a73fc5a0802388137b98f49","tid":1662732,"uid":48436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"話說！呢排不停宣傳香港人消費地圖，尋日突然有個廢老問我有無黃色酒樓，佢話想飲茶食點心。當我我完左各大地圖/List，先發覺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無黃色酒樓/點心店</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">酒樓飲茶文化</span></span>係香港人傳統文化！有無人介紹下？希望我睇漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係無？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有無有心有力人去開返間？</span></span>其實對文宣應該幾有幫助，d廢老未必個個識上連登。酒樓呢類佢經常去，又留得耐既地方，應該好容易向上一代做文宣！"},{"pid":"d61d67389945bc29bf58598e06d7103f5dbc8cc1","tid":1662732,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"上環周記？"},{"pid":"68e5eac64bb422f0c72cd0d0ffa8205a5f80fb07","tid":1662732,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:43:46.000Z","msg":"有無黃店放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bb46751c319feedd3642f7076cd8a6df07dfe8","tid":1662732,"uid":137344,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:49:13.000Z","msg":"因為酒樓嘅各式點心師傅都係典型中國撚<br />\n學師制又跪又拜又要聽聽話話<br />\n如果冇好大興趣/信念應該都係冇乜年輕人入行<br />\n而入咗行個啲接近全藍 廢老mode係咁屌 而且呢批人工時長唔點接受其他資訊 tvb係唯一途徑<br />\n你覺得可以黃得去邊"},{"pid":"d59d0df0c5da4a473c3d4c8846908f6bb3a2bad5","tid":1662732,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"港式茶餐廳，粉麵店都9成係藍色<br />\n<br />\n其實係好諷刺既一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}